  34,18,"We had also placed between them and the cities¬†We showered with blessings ňĻmany smallňļ towns within sight of one another. And We set moderate travel distances in between, ňĻsaying,ňļ ‚ÄúTravel between them by day and night safely.‚ÄĚ"
